WEBVTT

00:03.229 --> 00:05.100
Shop till you drop in Dubai,...

00:05.384 --> 00:08.428
...where you find the largest shopping malls in the world...

00:08.718 --> 00:11.203
...with an incredible variety of brands.

00:14.858 --> 00:17.553
For many visitors, the best authentic shopping...

00:17.891 --> 00:21.445
...is found in the city's traditional souks or markets.

00:21.755 --> 00:26.259
Two of Dubai's most famous markets are the Gold Souk and the Spice Souk.

